          "alertTitle": "Emerging Resistance",
          "details": "Previous CDC recommendations for dual therapy (Ceftriaxone + Azithromycin) were revised in 2020 to Ceftriaxone 500 mg IM alone due to increasing azithromycin resistance and stable resistance patterns to Ceftriaxone. Multiple drug resistance is increasing, with reports of strains resistant to both ceftriaxone and azithromycin."
        }
      ]
